  <brief_title>Safety and Efficacy of Bexagliflozin Compared to Glimepiride as Add-on Therapy to Metformin in Type 2 Diabetes Subjects</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Phase 3, Randomized, Double-blind, Active-controlled Study to Evaluate the Effects of Bexagliflozin Versus Glimepiride in Subjects With Type 2 Diabetes Mellitus Who Have Inadequate Glycemic Control by Metformin</official_title>
  <sponsors>
    <lead_sponsor>
